OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy outbreaks of rain in the
OL,6,Fwest with brisk winds. Drier in the
OL,7,Feast with bright spells, but breezy
OL,8,Fhere too. Temperatures around the
OL,9,Fseasonal average.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will slowly push east
OL,12,Fthis evening and overnight, gradually
OL,13,Fweakening. Clear spells at first in
OL,14,Fthe east with a few fog patches
OL,15,Fpossible. Cold and frosty in the north.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FRather cloudy across England
OL,18,Fand Wales with patchy outbreaks of
OL,19,Fdrizzle, but some brighter spells
OL,20,Fpossible too. Dry and largely sunny
OL,21,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
